OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779138669
OL,3,CBodies of four Italian scuba divers
OL,4,Cdiscovered in Maldives cave, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe bodies of four Italian divers who
OL,8,Fdied in a sea cave in the Maldives
OL,9,Flast week have been located, according
OL,10,Fto officials.
OL,12,FA tweet from the Maldives National
OL,13,FDefence Force on Monday said the
OL,14,Fbodies were "located inside the Vaavu
OL,15,Fatoll cave" and that "further dives
OL,16,Fwill be carried out in the coming
OL,17,Fdays" to recover them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
