PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779138669
OL,3,CBodies of four Italian scuba divers
OL,4,Cdiscovered in Maldives cave, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FSearches had resumed on Monday after
OL,8,Fbeing suspended following the death of
OL,9,FMohamed Mahudhee, a local military
OL,10,Fdiver, died during a rescue mission to
OL,11,Freach them.
OL,13,FFive Italian divers are believed to
OL,14,Fhave died while exploring a cave at a
OL,15,Fdepth of about 50 meters in Vaavu
OL,16,FAtoll on Thursday, according to
OL,17,FItaly's Foreign Ministry ` deeper than
OL,18,Fthe Maldives' recreational diving
OL,19,Flimit of 30 metres.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779138669
OL,3,CBodies of four Italian scuba divers
OL,4,Cdiscovered in Maldives cave, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe body of an Italian diving
OL,8,Finstructor had been found earlier
OL,9,Foutside the cave before the remaining
OL,10,Ffour divers were discovered.
OL,12,FThe victims have been identified as
OL,13,FMonica Montefalcone, an associate
OL,14,Fprofessor of ecology at the University
OL,15,Fof Genoa; her daughter, Giorgia
OL,16,FSommacal; marine biologist Federico
OL,17,FGualtieri; researcher Muriel Oddenino;
OL,18,Fand diving instructor Gianluca
OL,19,FBenedetti, according to the Maldivian
OL,20,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
