CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779138669
OL,3,CBodies of four Italian scuba divers
OL,4,Cdiscovered in Maldives cave, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FBenedetti's body was recovered last
OL,8,Fweek.
OL,10,FMaldives presidential spokesperson
OL,11,FMohamed Hussain Shareef said that
OL,12,FMahudhee, a member of the Maldivian
OL,13,FNational Defence Force, died of
OL,14,Funderwater decompression sickness
OL,15,Fafter being transferred to a hospital
OL,16,Fin the capital on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
