PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779138669
OL,3,CBodies of four Italian scuba divers
OL,4,Cdiscovered in Maldives cave, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FShareef said on Sunday that three
OL,8,FFinnish divers, experts in deep and
OL,9,Fcave diving, have arrived in the
OL,10,Farchipelago nation and joined the
OL,11,FMaldives coastguard in a meeting aimed
OL,12,Fat mapping a new search strategy.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FRough weather has repeatedly hampered
OL,20,Frescue efforts in the Indian Ocean.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
