FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779138669
OL,3,CBodies of four Italian scuba divers
OL,4,Cdiscovered in Maldives cave, officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FInitial teams had already dived to
OL,8,Fidentify and mark the entrance to the
OL,9,Fcave system where the Italians
OL,10,Fdisappeared. The cause of the deaths
OL,11,Fremains under investigation.
OL,13,FItaly's foreign ministry has been
OL,14,Fcoordinating with Divers Alert
OL,15,FNetwork, a specialist diving
OL,16,Forganisation, to support recovery
OL,17,Foperations and the repatriation of the
OL,18,Fbodies.
OL,20,FThe cause of the divers' deaths
OL,21,Fremains under investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
